text: Piruanycha itaiuba is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1997. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Piruanycha itaiuba. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1997
title: Piruanycha itaiuba
